msgctxt "6824"
msgid "新選組を抜けるつもりですか……　斎藤君。"
msgstr "Are you planning to leave the Shinsengumi ... Saito-kun."

msgctxt "6866"
msgid "土方……"
msgstr "Earthwork..."

msgctxt "6875"
msgid ""
"総司から話は聞きました。\n"
"あなたがここに来た理由も。本当の名前も全て。"
msgstr "I heard from Souji. Also why you came here. All the real names."

msgctxt "6947"
msgid "そうか……"
msgstr "Really……"

msgctxt "6959"
msgid "逃げんのかい。……一（はじめ）ちゃん。"
msgstr "Are you running away? ...... Ichi (beginning) -chan."

msgctxt "6999"
msgid "……逃げる？"
msgstr "……escape?"

msgctxt "7013"
msgid ""
"せや……　確かに一（はじめ）ちゃんが\n"
"新選組に居る理由は無ぅなった……"
msgstr ""
"Saya ... Certainly there is no reason why Ichi (Hajime) is in the "
"Shinsengumi ..."

msgctxt "7084"
msgid ""
"せやけどな、仲間残して独りで何もかも抱え込んで\n"
"闘いに向かうんは、逃げるっちゅうことや。"
msgstr ""
"It's a burn, but if you leave your friends and hold everything by yourself "
"and head for the fight, you'll have to run away."

msgctxt "7173"
msgid ""
"他人とつるまんと、独りでやる方がカッコええ……\n"
"せやけどそれじゃアカンのや。"
msgstr "It's cooler to do it alone with other people ... But then it's Akan."

msgctxt "7250"
msgid "闘いっちゅうんは、誰かと一緒にやらなアカンねん。"
msgstr "Fighting is an Akan that you can do with someone."

msgctxt "7300"
msgid "どうしてだ。"
msgstr "Why?"

msgctxt "7313"
msgid ""
"……人間、大事なことをする時は、誰かに\n"
"見ててもらわなアカンっちゅうことや。"
msgstr ""
"…… Human, when you do something important, you don't want someone to see "
"you."

msgctxt "7391"
msgid ""
"共に闘い、共に考え、共に哀しみ、共に喜ぶ……\n"
"そうやって時を同じくすることで、\n"
"事実は人から人へ伝わり歴史は作られてく。"
msgstr ""
"Fighting together, thinking together, sadness together, rejoicing together "
"... By doing so at the same time, the facts are transmitted from person to "
"person and history is created."

msgctxt "7512"
msgid ""
"せやから近藤局長は、最期まで新選組という\n"
"仲間を捨てなかったんや。"
msgstr "Director General Kondo did not abandon the Shinsengumi until the end."

msgctxt "7579"
msgid ""
"だが、俺はこれ以上、新選組を巻き込むわけには\n"
"いかない……　ここから先は、坂本龍馬という\n"
"１人の男としての闘いだ。"
msgstr ""
"However, I can't get involved in the Shinsengumi anymore ... From here on, "
"it's a fight as a man named Ryoma Sakamoto."

msgctxt "7694"
msgid ""
"それがどないした。\n"
"……坂本龍馬１人の闘いのために新選組が闘う。\n"
"それでええやないか。"
msgstr ""
"It didn't work. ...... Ryoma Sakamoto The Shinsengumi fights for the fight "
"of one person. Isn't that so?"

msgctxt "7781"
msgid "沖田……"
msgstr "Okita ……"

msgctxt "7790"
msgid "な、新八？"
msgstr "What, Shinpachi?"

msgctxt "7801"
msgid ""
"ああ。\n"
"俺にとっちゃ、それが局長と共に生きるということ\n"
"でもあるしな。"
msgstr "Oh. For me, that also means living with the director."

msgctxt "7873"
msgid "永倉……"
msgstr "Nagakura ……"

msgctxt "7884"
msgid "土方……"
msgstr "Earthwork..."

msgctxt "7894"
msgid ""
"それに坂本さん……\n"
"あなたの斎藤一としての仕事はまだ残って\n"
"いるようだ。"
msgstr ""
"And Mr. Sakamoto ... It seems that your work as Saito Hajime still remains."

msgctxt "7967"
msgid ""
"仕事？\n"
"近藤はそこに最後の策があると言っていたが……"
msgstr "jobs? Kondo said that there was a last resort ..."

msgctxt "8020"
msgid ""
"近藤勇は死んでも死なん……か。\n"
"……フッ。"
msgstr "Isami Kondo is dead even if he dies ...? ...... Huh."

